# QGIS summary

## Goal
Recreate the PowerBI choropleth map using QGIS

## Summary

- The join between the socioeconomic database and the shapefile was performed using the *canton* field. There were no matching issues, thanks to the editing of the datasets.

- The CRTM05 (official CRS for Costa Rica) was used.

- The map allowed to view the distribution of growth type *cantones*, mostly the concentration of *cantones* in decline in the north of the country, and over at the Caribbean coast.

